Installation Instructions
=========================

Create a target folder and copy wizards/update-ftl.sh to it.
Then enter the target folder and run the update script.
Your system must provide:
	* cmake (>2.8)
	* g++ (>3.3.6)
	* gnumake
	* a bash shell

Check the header of the build script for build options.
You can place an update-options.sh into the same folder to
override options.
